			<p>
				Customers who are businesses and organizations (not applicable to individual customers) when buying a complete computer (including: laptop, assembled computer, synchronous machine) at Hanoi Computer Company get 1 free GOLDEN WARRANTY CARDS worth 500,000 VND (warranty at the place of use) for each product.
			</p>
			<br>
			<p>
				Gold warranty card (TBHV) is a service card for repairing computers, components and IT products issued by Hanu Computer Company.
			</p>
			<br>
			<p>
				The card is not redeemable for cash and is only issued once per product. The Company does not re-issue in case of loss, damage or expiration of the card.
			</p>
			<br>
			<p>
				Each card is valid for 12 months from the date of issue. Within that period, the customer is allowed to use up to 10 times the service/card with all the customer's products.
			</p>
			<br>
			<p>
				Customers with Golden card have the right to choose the Warranty location: At the Company's Warranty Department, or choose the form of warranty at the place of use within a radius of 20 Km from the sales location of Hanu Computer Company.
